Perfect for finding personal space from your family during the holidays. 

@aidesign.png brings us #biomimicry, which is by definition: the design and production of materials, structures, and systems that are modeled on biological entities and processes. 

Photos by @aidesign.png https://t.co/9Ww6x061h4

@federicocinaofficial is fueled by the mission to create sustainable garments within their hometown of Romagna, Italy. Italian-inspired rusty pinks and nudes flow through the #SS23 collection. 

Photos by @gabrielerosati_
